Still on security of the nation the government is monitoring and evaluating the country security status ahead of next year&rsquo;s general election&hellip;the national Security Council has identified possible hotspots that may need attention before the polls. Interior CS Dr Fred Matiangi is warning perpetrators of hate speech that the long arm of the law will catch up with them. Matiangi was speaking during the official launch of the NCIC strategic plan.
